DataElement.preferredName: Protocol Agent Transfer Administration Performed Study Activity Actual Date and Time Range ISO21090.IVL.TS.DATETIME.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The completed action in which an authorized party at a designated study site dispenses or receives a study agent to/from a study subject. EXAMPLE(S): StudySubject receives a bottle of pills. The date and time span when this activity began and ended. EXAMPLE(S): The date and time when a sample is taken from the subject. A dose of chemotherapy is given on June 12th starting at 9am and finishing at 12pm.
